{
  "stem": "7458.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And we survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "There was one other, a fourth one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And the four of us were hiding out in barns with farmers in the forest until we were liberated-- early 1945.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "In order to survive in the forest-- the forests were not so large, and farmers would come through them, and Germans would come through them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And we knew that if we were to survive, we would have to have hiding places.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "So we actually built a hole in the ground, a bunker in the forest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And there again, I don't have a drawing of that yet, because it's part of the story where I haven't reached yet in my memoirs, but I will.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And we built with nothing more than an ax, a shovel, and a couple of empty bags from potatoes-- you know, those burlap bags.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "We managed to build a beautiful bunker in the forest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "We did it twice actually.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "What we would do is we would find an area in the forest where there were lots of large trees, but also a few small ones, young trees, not too heavy to lift out.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "We would dig out one of those little trees with a cone going this way, like a pumpkin, when you carve a pumpkin, the top, so that it would not fall in.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "That would hold the roots of the tree and a ball of earth.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "We would lift that out gently, put it aside.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "Then, we dug a hole for the four of us about six feet long, about four feet deep, and about four feet wide, or six feet wide maybe.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And we found pieces of pipe that we put into the corners.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "We also dug around a larger area around this six by four hole.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
